+## Technical Details
+
+### Recommendation Heuristics (Priority Order)
+1. No selected job ΓåÆ Recommend selecting or searching
+2. Missing pay range/location ΓåÆ Recommend verifying details
+3. Grade level mismatch ΓåÆ Recommend targeting closer match
+4. Location mismatch ΓåÆ Recommend checking location
+5. Work arrangement mismatch ΓåÆ Recommend verifying arrangement
+6. Strong match (2+ signals) ΓåÆ Recommend proceeding with application
+7. Partial match ΓåÆ Recommend tailoring approach
+
+### Confidence Levels
+- **Low**: Limited data, generic advice
+- **Medium**: Some signals present, reasonable advice
+- **High**: Strong signals, specific advice
+
+### Action Routing
+- `/dashboard/job-search`: Navigate to job search
+- `/dashboard/resume`: Navigate to resume builder
+- `/dashboard/saved-jobs`: Navigate to saved jobs
+- Falls back to job search for unknown intents
